    "text": {
      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">People</a> * Marco Belli</b>\n</p><p><b>Marco Belli</b>,<br />\nan Italian computer chess programmer and author of the <a href=\"/UCI\" title=\"UCI\">UCI</a> compliant chess engines <a href=\"/Vajolet\" title=\"Vajolet\">Vajolet</a> and <a href=\"/Vajolet#2\" title=\"Vajolet\">Vajolet2</a>. \nAfter early chess programming trials in <a href=\"/C_sharp\" title=\"C sharp\">C#</a>, Marco worked through <a href=\"/index.php?title=Stef_Luijten&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Stef Luijten (page does not exist)\">Stef Luijten's</a> tutorial on <a href=\"/Winglet\" title=\"Winglet\">Winglet</a>, <i>Writing a Chess Program in 99 Steps</i> <sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>, and created his second engine in <a href=\"/Cpp\" title=\"Cpp\">C++</a>, already forerunner of Vajolet2 <sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Forum_Posts\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Forum Posts</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#2010_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2010 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#2015_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2015 ...</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#External_Links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External Links</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Forum_Posts\">Forum Posts</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Marco_Belli&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Forum Posts\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2010_...\">2010 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Marco_Belli&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: 2010 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=34545\">Vajolet Chess Engine</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Marco Belli</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, May 27, 2010</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=43165\">futility pruning, razoring question</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Marco Belli</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, April 04, 2012&#160;» <a href=\"/Futility_Pruning\" title=\"Futility Pruning\">Futility Pruning</a>, <a href=\"/Razoring\" title=\"Razoring\">Razoring</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=48996\">uci ponder protocol</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Marco Belli</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, August 17, 2013&#160;» <a href=\"/UCI\" title=\"UCI\">UCI</a>, <a href=\"/Pondering\" title=\"Pondering\">Pondering</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=49316\">polyglot en passant square</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Marco Belli</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, September 12, 2013&#160;» <a href=\"/En_passant\" title=\"En passant\">En passant</a>, <a href=\"/PolyGlot\" title=\"PolyGlot\">PolyGlot</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=50472\">floating point SSE eval</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Marco Belli</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, December 13, 2013&#160;» <a href=\"/Evaluation\" title=\"Evaluation\">Evaluation</a>, <a href=\"/Float\" title=\"Float\">Float</a>, <a href=\"/Score\" title=\"Score\">Score</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=51302\">where can I make my engine play against human?</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Marco Belli</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, February 16, 2014</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=51786\">Vajolet2 released</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Marco Belli</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, March 29, 2014</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=52226\">transposition and multithreading question</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Marco Belli</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, May 04, 2014&#160;» <a href=\"/Transposition_Table\" title=\"Transposition Table\">Transposition Table</a>, <a href=\"/Parallel_Search\" title=\"Parallel Search\">Parallel Search</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=53220\">advanced tapered evalutation</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Marco Belli</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, August 08, 2014&#160;» <a href=\"/SSE\" title=\"SSE\">SSE</a>, <a href=\"/Tapered_Eval\" title=\"Tapered Eval\">Tapered Eval</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2015_...\">2015 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Marco_Belli&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: 2015 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=56086\">Vajolet2 2.0 released</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Marco Belli</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, April 21, 2015</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=56363\">how to probe egtb from console?</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Marco Belli</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, May 15, 2015&#160;» <a href=\"/Endgame_Tablebases\" title=\"Endgame Tablebases\">Endgame Tablebases</a>, <a href=\"/CLI\" title=\"CLI\">CLI</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=58645\">lazy smp questions</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Marco Belli</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, December 21, 2015&#160;» <a href=\"/Lazy_SMP\" title=\"Lazy SMP\">Lazy SMP</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=66221\">tuning info</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Marco Belli</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, January 03, 2018&#160;» <a href=\"/Automated_Tuning\" title=\"Automated Tuning\">Automated Tuning</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_Links\">External Links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Marco_Belli&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: External Links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://github.com/elcabesa\">elcabesa · GitHub</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://code.google.com/u/elcabesa/\">elcabesa Google Project Hosting</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://vajoletchess.blogspot.it/\">vajoletChess Blog</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Marco_Belli&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://web.archive.org/web/20120621100214/http://www.sluijten.com/winglet/\">Winglet, Writing a Chess Program in 99 Steps</a> by <a href=\"/index.php?title=Stef_Luijten&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Stef Luijten (page does not exist)\">Stef Luijten</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wayback_Machine\">Wayback Machine</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-2\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=52709&amp;start=18\">Re: where to start chess programming?</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Marco Belli</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, June 22, 2014</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div>\n<p><b><a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">Up one level</a></b>\n</p>\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260228094859\nCache expiry: 86400\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.008 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.008 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 51/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 106/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 0/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 0/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 2/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,c